summary: My currect character, so i thought i might share her.
descriptionHtml:
Hello!

this my second preset for skyrim, and hopefully you [i]enjoy[/i] my preset.

[size=6]Introduction
[/size]Hikah is a sneaky character, who prefers light armour and weaponry. She is an nord elf halflin. She is especially skilled with normal swords, and has an affinity for restoration magic. But none of that matter since 80% of people only play this game cause of [i][url=http://www.dictionary.com/browse/degenerate]intercourse labratory[/url][/i]


[size=5]HOW TO USE[/size]
[size=2]1) Open your console (For me it's ½)
[/size]
2) type 'showracemenu'

3) Set your race to nord

4) navigate to the preset tab, and load up my preset.

[size=5]Requirements; all requirements must be met, no matter the version.
[/size]
